@page "/"

<PageTitle>Wassel | Gestion E-commerce Algérie</PageTitle>

<div class="landing-page" data-testid="landing-page">
    <section class="hero-panel">
        <div class="hero-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">Plateforme E-commerce Algérie</p>
            <h1>Centralisez vos commandes. Confirmez. Expédiez.</h1>
            <p class="hero-text">
                Wassel unifie toutes vos sources de commandes - Facebook, WhatsApp, Instagram, 
                Google Sheets - dans un tableau de bord unique optimisé pour le Cash on Delivery.
            </p>

            <div class="cta-row">
                <NavLink class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/login" data-testid="cta-login">Commencer maintenant</NavLink>
                <NavLink class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href="/register" data-testid="cta-register">Créer un compte</NavLink>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-pills" aria-label="Fonctionnalités">
                <span>COD First</span>
                <span>58 Wilayas</span>
                <span>Multi-sources</span>
                <span>Français / عربي</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="preview-card">
            <div class="preview-card__header">
                <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow">Aperçu en direct</p>
                    <h2>Dashboard opérationnel</h2>
                </div>
                <span class="mini-chip">Live</span>
            </div>

            <div class="preview-stats">
                <div>
                    <strong>128</strong>
                    <span>commandes/jour</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <strong>87%</strong>
                    <span>confirmées</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <strong>58</strong>
                    <span>wilayas</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mini-board">
                <div class="mini-board__row">
                    <span class="source-chip source-chip--whatsapp">WhatsApp</span>
                    <span>#83047</span>
                    <span class="status-chip status-chip--pending">En attente</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-board__row">
                    <span class="source-chip source-chip--facebook">Facebook</span>
                    <span>#83046</span>
                    <span class="status-chip status-chip--confirm">Confirmé</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-board__row">
                    <span class="source-chip source-chip--manual">Manuel</span>
                    <span>#83045</span>
                    <span class="status-chip status-chip--ship">Expédié</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="features-grid" data-testid="features-section">
        <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
            <h3>Multi-Sources</h3>
            <p>Capturez automatiquement les commandes depuis Facebook, WhatsApp, Instagram et Google Sheets.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
            <h3>Workflow COD</h3>
            <p>Statuts adaptés au marché algérien: En attente → Confirmé → Expédié → Livré.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🚚</div>
            <h3>Livraison intégrée</h3>
            <p>Yalidine, ZR Express, Maystro, EcoTrack - tous vos transporteurs en un clic.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
            <h3>Analytics temps réel</h3>
            <p>Taux de confirmation, livraison, retours - suivez vos KPIs en direct.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">👥</div>
            <h3>Multi-utilisateurs</h3>
            <p>Agents, coordinateurs, propriétaires - chaque rôle a ses permissions.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🗺️</div>
            <h3>58 Wilayas</h3>
            <p>Base de données complète des wilayas et communes algériennes intégrée.</p>
        </article>
    </section>

    <section class="delivery-section">
        <h2>Transporteurs partenaires</h2>
        <div class="delivery-logos">
            <div class="delivery-logo">
                <strong>Yalidine</strong>
                <span>Livraison rapide</span>
            </div>
            <div class="delivery-logo">
                <strong>ZR Express</strong>
                <span>Couverture nationale</span>
            </div>
            <div class="delivery-logo">
                <strong>Maystro</strong>
                <span>Stop desk & domicile</span>
            </div>
            <div class="delivery-logo">
                <strong>EcoTrack</strong>
                <span>Suivi temps réel</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
    .source-chip--whatsapp {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #25d366, #128c7e);
    }
    
    .source-chip--facebook {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1877f2, #0d65d9);
    }
    
    .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 1.25rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .feature-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: rgba(10, 16, 30, 0.78);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(140, 77, 255, 0.3);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .feature-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .feature-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(238, 243, 255, 0.7);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    
    .delivery-section {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .delivery-section h2 {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .delivery-logos {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .delivery-logo {
        padding: 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }
    
    .delivery-logo strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    
    .delivery-logo span {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: rgba(238, 243, 255, 0.6);
    }
    
    @@media (max-width: 900px) {
        .features-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
        
        .delivery-logos {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
    }
    
    @@media (max-width: 600px) {
        .features-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        
        .delivery-logos {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
